Soloing named in BOT with COD was not something only the elite enchanters could do, it was common and hardly uberly difficult. Sure there is danger in doing it but a lot of the mini  boss's are right next a 'zone' so charm breaks and you just bail to the zone. 50% of the time you wouldnt make it but hey <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
