COD (not charm) needed nerfing. This latest nerf IMHO didnt go far enough. To bring it into balance I feel it would have been better to make it like dictate. Fixed duration with a recast on it. Make it last 2 mins with a 5 min recast or something. <p>Sage Chantasha Sim'Li<br>
